_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#props","content":"The NumberField component accepts the following props:"},"491":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-16","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#basic","content":"Minimal usage with label, placeholder, and min/max."},"492":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-17","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#controlled","content":"Use `value` and `onChange` for controlled state."},"493":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-18","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#invalid","content":"Use `isInvalid` with `errorMessage` for validation feedback."},"494":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-19","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#disabled","content":"Use `isDisabled` to prevent input."},"495":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-20","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#hide-stepper","content":"Use `hideStepper` to show only the input without +/- buttons."},"496":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-21","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#value-scale","content":"Use `minValue`, `maxValue`, and `step` to set the allowed values. Steps are calculated from the minimum value."},"497":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-22","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#format-options-numbering-system","content":"By default, NumberField displays the value using the numbering system for the user's locale. Use the `formatOptions` prop to override the numbering system by setting the Unicode numbering system locale extension."},"498":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-23","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#keyboard","content":"When focus is in the input (and the field is not read-only), keyboard behavior follows common spinbutton-style conventions:"},"499":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-24","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#keyboard","content":"**Arrow Up** / **Arrow Down** (or **Up** / **Down**): increase or decrease by `step`"},"500":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-25","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#keyboard","content":"**Page Up** / **Page Down**: larger increase or decrease when supported"},"501":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-26","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#keyboard","content":"**Home** / **End**: jump to `minValue` or `maxValue` when those props are set"},"502":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-27","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#keyboard","content":"Stepper buttons are real buttons and follow standard button keyboard activation. Use &#x2A;*`incrementAriaLabel`*&#x2A; and &#x2A;*`decrementAriaLabel`** when the default labels are not enough in your locale or UI."},"503":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-28","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#aria-and-labeling","content":"The input is associated with the visible label and optional description and error content for assistive technologies."},"504":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-29","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#aria-and-labeling","content":"Invalid and required states are exposed to assistive technologies when you use `isInvalid`, `errorMessage`, and `isRequired`."},"505":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-30","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#aria-and-labeling","content":"Set &#x2A;*`isWheelDisabled`** if the value should not change when the user scrolls with a pointer wheel while the field is focused."},"506":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-31","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#best-practices","content":"Pair &#x2A;*`isInvalid`*&#x2A; with &#x2A;*`errorMessage`** so users get both visual and programmatic feedback."},"507":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-32","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#best-practices","content":"Remember valid steps start from &#x2A;*`minValue`**."},"508":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-33","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#best-practices","content":"Use &#x2A;*`isDisabled`*&#x2A; when the value cannot be changed; use &#x2A;*`isReadOnly`** when the value should be visible but not editable. Do not use them interchangeably."},"509":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-34","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#best-practices","content":"For currency or units, ensure &#x2A;*`formatOptions`** (and locale) match what users are allowed to type."},"510":{"id":"/docs/components/pagination","page_id":"/docs/components/pagination","type":"page","content":"Pagination","breadcrumbs":["Docs","Components"],"tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/pagination"},"511":{"id":"/docs/components/pagination-0","page_id":"/docs/components/pagination","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/pagination","content":"A pagination component with prev/next buttons and dot indicators, configurable page limits, and optional visibility of contr